WEBVTT

01:37.920 --> 01:41.009
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.080 --> 01:43.950
[Episode 30]

02:10.840 --> 02:14.360
Actually, I'm quite afraid
you'll regret coming to Hong Kong with me.

02:14.360 --> 02:15.210
Why?

02:15.830 --> 02:18.160
I'm afraid you were just being impulsive.

02:18.620 --> 02:20.150
I was just being impulsive.

02:25.730 --> 02:27.410
So sometimes acting on impulse

02:27.410 --> 02:29.300
doesn't seem like a bad thing.

02:30.740 --> 02:31.890
What do you mean?

02:32.100 --> 02:33.690
Are you not happy today?

02:34.670 --> 02:35.670
I am happy.

02:36.510 --> 02:39.060
And I haven't been
this happy in a long time.

02:39.400 --> 02:40.070
Really?

02:43.190 --> 02:44.840
And I feel like today

02:46.010 --> 02:47.940
you're a bit different from usual.

02:52.770 --> 02:54.050
Is that good or bad?

02:54.990 --> 02:55.870
Take a guess.

03:01.220 --> 03:03.910
Every side of you is so attractive to me.

03:44.430 --> 03:45.360
I'm sorry.

03:48.170 --> 03:49.900
I'm the one who should be sorry.

04:15.640 --> 04:18.380
I thought I could just let loose for a bit

04:19.110 --> 04:20.230
and treat this trip

04:20.250 --> 04:22.180
as a reward for myself,

04:23.600 --> 04:24.920
relying on my most instinctual impulses

04:24.920 --> 04:26.630
to accept the man beside me.

04:27.750 --> 04:29.360
But it wasn't until I pushed him away

04:29.360 --> 04:30.360
that I realized

04:30.970 --> 04:32.830
no matter how much I try to escape,

04:33.270 --> 04:34.880
I can't deceive myself.

04:56.240 --> 04:57.830
Good morning, everyone.

04:58.680 --> 04:59.360
Ms. Xu.

04:59.680 --> 05:01.190
How was it? Was Hong Kong fun?

05:01.190 --> 05:02.270
Is that even a question?

05:02.270 --> 05:04.190
Just look at Ms. Xu today.

05:04.190 --> 05:06.240
The trip to Hong Kong
was definitely worth it.

05:06.240 --> 05:08.190
Could you two stop gossiping so much?

05:08.190 --> 05:08.820
Right.

05:08.850 --> 05:11.280
Someone just sent over
two invitation letters.

05:11.280 --> 05:12.230
One is for you,

05:12.260 --> 05:13.720
and the other is for Mr. Ji.

05:14.180 --> 05:16.180
It seems there's some kind of event.

05:15.070 --> 05:16.260
[I Sincerely Invite You to a Unique]

05:16.290 --> 05:17.400
[Jazz-Themed Gathering, By Marcos Yang]

05:17.630 --> 05:18.430
Ms. Xu.

05:18.430 --> 05:20.750
If you are going to see Mr. Ji later,

05:20.870 --> 05:22.580
could you bring this to him for me?

05:22.580 --> 05:24.070
I will not be seeing Mr. Ji later.

05:24.070 --> 05:25.390
Tell him to come get it himself.

05:25.390 --> 05:28.190
-Okay.
-Ms. Xu, you're needed in the banquet hall.

05:28.790 --> 05:30.390
Okay, I'm coming right away.

05:31.000 --> 05:31.750
Mr. Ji.

05:33.790 --> 05:34.670
Good morning.

05:38.030 --> 05:38.870
Mr. Ji,

05:38.900 --> 05:41.700
someone just brought you
this invitation letter.

05:41.850 --> 05:42.920
Okay. I got it.

05:55.940 --> 05:58.490
Marcos said
it's a private gathering of his.

05:58.620 --> 06:00.350
He hopes to thank you in person.

06:01.500 --> 06:02.250
I will go.

06:06.750 --> 06:09.410
I heard you went to
Hong Kong these past few days.

06:10.660 --> 06:11.900
Did it rain there?

06:13.560 --> 06:14.390
No.

06:17.000 --> 06:19.060
Then the weather forecast was wrong.

06:20.280 --> 06:21.940
It's good that it didn't rain.

06:26.860 --> 06:28.150
You just recovered.

06:28.750 --> 06:30.750
Be careful not to catch a cold again.

06:50.180 --> 06:52.420
Mr. Peng! Mr. Peng!

06:52.630 --> 06:53.430
Wait!

06:54.720 --> 06:56.060
Please give us another chance.

06:56.060 --> 06:56.950
Mr. Peng!

07:00.000 --> 07:00.880
Mr. Peng!

07:10.920 --> 07:12.070
Why didn't you stop

07:12.070 --> 07:13.960
such an important client from leaving?

07:13.960 --> 07:15.110
I'm sorry, Mr. Duan.

07:15.190 --> 07:15.870
I...

07:16.450 --> 07:17.040
Get lost.

07:17.070 --> 07:18.090
I don't want to see you again.

07:18.090 --> 07:18.980
I'm sorry.

07:47.190 --> 07:48.080
Mr. Duan Jr.

07:54.720 --> 07:56.040
I didn't expect

07:56.070 --> 07:58.530
you'd look pretty cool
riding a motorcycle.

07:58.750 --> 08:00.610
There's a lot you'd never expect.

08:01.560 --> 08:02.620
Are we going or not?

08:03.270 --> 08:04.070
Where to?

08:04.510 --> 08:05.820
I'm really popular right now.

08:05.820 --> 08:08.820
It'll be troublesome
if I get recognized when I go out.

08:08.870 --> 08:10.050
Going for a motorcycle ride.

08:10.050 --> 08:11.110
Want to come along?

08:11.690 --> 08:12.500
Wait.

08:13.200 --> 08:15.430
Why are you suddenly so attentive today?

08:15.430 --> 08:16.600
Is it that guy Ji Feng

08:16.600 --> 08:17.930
who sent you to spy on me?

08:23.920 --> 08:25.020
You're so slow and naggy.

08:25.020 --> 08:26.080
Hurry up and get on.

08:27.730 --> 08:30.540
Since you begged me
so much to accompany you,

08:30.570 --> 08:33.090
I'll reluctantly go with you.

08:55.650 --> 08:58.390
How is it? Feeling better?

08:58.540 --> 09:00.200
Who said I was in a bad mood?

09:00.510 --> 09:01.640
Don't overthink it.

09:01.860 --> 09:05.000
Fine, I'm the one in a bad mood, okay?

09:09.900 --> 09:10.740
Pull over.

09:11.770 --> 09:12.750
What's wrong?

09:13.520 --> 09:15.590
Stop! I'm going to throw up.

09:16.070 --> 09:17.120
Don't throw up.

09:17.120 --> 09:18.740
Don't throw up in my helmet.

09:34.220 --> 09:37.280
Why didn't you tell me
you get motion sickness earlier?

09:38.780 --> 09:39.870
Don't tell anyone.

09:41.780 --> 09:43.660
I have leverage over you now.

09:50.080 --> 09:51.320
Why is it that every time

09:51.320 --> 09:52.720
I encounter such a mess

09:52.720 --> 09:53.790
I bump into you?

09:54.600 --> 09:56.960
Is this considered fate?

09:59.250 --> 10:00.710
What are you trying to say?

10:01.200 --> 10:02.630
I'm trying to say...

10:04.330 --> 10:06.420
Should I take over a barbecue place?

10:08.020 --> 10:10.580
The big star is taking
a down-to-earth route?

10:10.600 --> 10:11.810
What do you know?

10:12.200 --> 10:14.240
This is called investing in my hobbies.

10:14.240 --> 10:15.770
Since this didn't work out,

10:15.910 --> 10:18.020
maybe I'll have better luck
with the barbecue place

10:18.020 --> 10:19.180
and make it big?

10:20.340 --> 10:22.410
Then I'll let you be my Chef.

10:22.820 --> 10:24.490
You... you just grill

10:24.520 --> 10:26.270
those things you grilled

10:26.270 --> 10:28.670
at the party last time.

10:29.910 --> 10:31.240
What makes you think

10:31.240 --> 10:34.120
I would give up being
a Chef at a five-star hotel

10:34.510 --> 10:36.390
to work at your barbecue stand?

10:36.390 --> 10:38.050
I'm personally inviting you.

10:38.120 --> 10:39.180
Isn't that enough?

10:41.000 --> 10:41.670
At worst,

10:41.670 --> 10:43.790
I'll give you the naming rights

10:43.790 --> 10:44.620
to the barbecue restaurant.

10:44.620 --> 10:46.750
You can name it whatever you want then.

10:47.030 --> 10:49.640
Like Chef Qiao,

10:49.670 --> 10:52.670
or Qiaoqi's Selection.

10:52.790 --> 10:53.840
Duan Aoxiang,

10:53.860 --> 10:55.570
are you trying to hit on me?

11:02.670 --> 11:03.790
What if I say yes?

11:04.480 --> 11:05.680
How would you answer?

11:09.030 --> 11:10.230
It depends on my mood.

11:12.700 --> 11:14.730
What does that mean?

11:14.910 --> 11:15.910
It means

11:16.210 --> 11:17.860
it depends on my mood.

11:18.640 --> 11:19.430
I'm leaving.

11:53.550 --> 11:54.240
Kenny.

11:54.960 --> 11:55.760
Over here.

11:56.870 --> 11:57.150
Marcos.

11:57.150 --> 11:58.550
Thank you for coming.

11:58.580 --> 11:59.700
Come here.

12:01.030 --> 12:01.870
Everyone,

12:01.870 --> 12:03.490
this is my very good friend.

12:03.610 --> 12:05.750
A famous hotel manager.

12:06.700 --> 12:09.370
Ji Feng, general manager of Purong Hotel.

12:09.390 --> 12:11.000
Nice to meet you.

12:11.200 --> 12:11.960
Marcos.

12:11.990 --> 12:13.630
Do you also cooperate with Purong Hotel?

12:13.630 --> 12:14.500
Of course.

12:14.520 --> 12:16.760
Purong's service is extremely thoughtful.

12:16.760 --> 12:19.090
And after we established
our cooperation back then,

12:19.090 --> 12:21.330
I found that Kenny and I
got along really well.

12:21.330 --> 12:22.740
Marcos really gives us a lot of face,

12:22.740 --> 12:25.580
generously promoting our Purong Hotel.

12:25.640 --> 12:26.160
It's my pleasure.

12:26.160 --> 12:27.730
We are a bit flattered.

12:29.840 --> 12:30.720
Where is Ms. Xu?

12:31.530 --> 12:32.730
I forgot to tell you.

12:32.770 --> 12:34.320
She is the lobby manager now,

12:34.320 --> 12:36.430
and has to handle many things herself.

12:36.430 --> 12:38.370
She's probably tied up with hotel matters.

12:38.370 --> 12:39.180
Okay.

12:43.040 --> 12:43.920
Ms. Xu.

13:06.850 --> 13:07.720
Ms. Xu.

13:08.120 --> 13:09.710
Long time no see, Mr. Yang.

13:10.230 --> 13:11.500
You look

13:12.370 --> 13:13.500
so beautiful today.

13:13.730 --> 13:14.550
Thank you.

13:14.820 --> 13:16.370
I should be the one thanking you.

13:16.370 --> 13:17.910
My grandfather has now remembered

13:17.910 --> 13:19.220
many things from the past.

13:19.220 --> 13:21.570
His condition has improved a lot.

13:21.640 --> 13:22.390
Most importantly,

13:22.390 --> 13:24.840
he is now willing to share with me

13:24.840 --> 13:26.510
the stories from his youth

13:26.510 --> 13:27.790
when he was in China.

13:28.730 --> 13:30.780
This is all thanks to you.

13:31.330 --> 13:32.520
That's wonderful.

13:32.550 --> 13:33.710
Congratulations.

13:34.570 --> 13:35.360
Thank you.

13:38.150 --> 13:40.030
By the way, I just heard Kenny say

13:40.030 --> 13:42.870
that you've been
promoted to lobby manager.

13:43.520 --> 13:44.270
Congratulations.

13:44.270 --> 13:44.870
Thank you.

13:44.870 --> 13:46.720
I knew Kenny

13:46.870 --> 13:49.070
would never overlook a talent like you.

13:49.270 --> 13:51.930
It's because Ms. Xu
has outstanding abilities,

13:51.970 --> 13:54.260
and Purong Hotel is
exactly in need of talent.

13:54.260 --> 13:55.440
You know, Marcos,

13:55.550 --> 13:57.270
for both employees and the company,

13:57.270 --> 13:58.900
they need to help each other succeed.

13:58.900 --> 13:59.870
That's true.

14:00.720 --> 14:03.200
Then let me congratulate the two of you.

14:04.510 --> 14:05.120
Come on, cheers.

14:05.120 --> 14:06.150
Thank you.

14:08.270 --> 14:09.030
By the way,

14:09.090 --> 14:11.680
how about I introduce
some friends from our side?

14:11.680 --> 14:12.320
Sure.

14:12.340 --> 14:13.220
Come, let's go.

14:16.200 --> 14:16.960
Hello.

14:16.980 --> 14:18.320
These two are my friends,

14:18.320 --> 14:19.790
Miyu and Ji Feng.

14:20.190 --> 14:21.310
They are both from Purong Hotel.

14:21.310 --> 14:22.410
Nice to meet you.

14:22.960 --> 14:24.820
You can come if you have a holiday.

14:30.340 --> 14:31.440
Nice to meet you.

14:31.470 --> 14:33.600
This is Miyu and Ji Feng.

14:33.600 --> 14:34.320
They are both my friends.

14:34.320 --> 14:35.640
Miyu, Ji Feng.

14:35.930 --> 14:36.860
Nice to meet you.

14:40.480 --> 14:41.740
How is the party today?

14:42.210 --> 14:43.170
It is okay?

14:43.200 --> 14:44.080
Not bad.

14:44.760 --> 14:46.150
Is the AC too strong?

14:46.180 --> 14:47.060
It's a bit cold.

14:47.590 --> 14:48.660
I'm going to the restroom.

14:48.660 --> 14:49.860
Don't drink too much.

14:53.590 --> 14:55.720
There's food over there too.

14:55.740 --> 14:57.190
You can go and have some.

14:58.760 --> 15:03.840
[Tan Jizhou]

15:01.280 --> 15:03.170
Miyu, I've arrived in Shanghai.

15:03.200 --> 15:04.390
Can we meet?

15:16.520 --> 15:17.120
Kenny.

15:17.470 --> 15:18.060
What's up?

15:18.060 --> 15:19.590
I want to ask you a question.

15:20.660 --> 15:23.100
Do you like Ms. Xu?

15:24.570 --> 15:26.300
Why do you think so?

15:26.470 --> 15:28.740
I saw you looking at her all night.

15:28.810 --> 15:31.330
Your eyes hardly left her.

15:31.440 --> 15:32.570
It's quite obvious.

15:33.490 --> 15:34.470
Marcos.

15:35.080 --> 15:35.800
Yeah.

15:35.970 --> 15:36.670
I do like her.

15:36.670 --> 15:38.210
Is there a problem?

15:44.430 --> 15:46.550
If you like her, tell her.

15:46.580 --> 15:48.230
Let her know how you feel.

15:48.260 --> 15:49.100
Right?

15:49.320 --> 15:50.180
How about this?

15:50.330 --> 15:53.120
There's a dance session coming up.

15:53.150 --> 15:55.130
Take this chance to ask her out.

15:57.180 --> 15:58.020
Give it a try.

16:15.520 --> 16:16.330
Excuse me.

16:16.560 --> 16:18.450
Are you here alone?

16:19.420 --> 16:20.300
No.

16:21.440 --> 16:22.130
Then,

16:22.850 --> 16:24.110
where is your partner?

16:24.370 --> 16:25.830
How could he have the heart to

16:25.830 --> 16:27.620
leave someone as beautiful as you alone?

16:27.620 --> 16:29.150
Is there anything you need?

16:30.720 --> 16:32.380
The dancing is about to start.

16:32.520 --> 16:35.140
I'd like to ask you for a dance.

16:35.700 --> 16:36.450
I'm afraid I'm not available.

16:36.450 --> 16:38.380
Please find someone else, thanks.

16:38.870 --> 16:39.740
Miss.

16:45.360 --> 16:46.290
Excuse me.

16:46.690 --> 16:48.150
She already has a partner.

16:52.360 --> 16:53.240
Sorry.

16:58.100 --> 16:58.740
Thank you.

16:59.340 --> 17:00.140
It's nothing.

17:10.329 --> 17:11.200
Are you okay?

17:13.140 --> 17:13.780
I'm fine.

17:32.060 --> 17:33.390
Why aren't you dancing?

17:37.520 --> 17:38.490
Do you want to?

18:11.350 --> 18:12.450
After this,

18:12.710 --> 18:13.840
what are your plans?

18:14.880 --> 18:17.450
What's wrong? Something up at the hotel?

18:18.120 --> 18:19.360
I want to ask you out.

18:22.390 --> 18:24.050
Stop saying things like that.

18:24.520 --> 18:25.780
Then do you

18:25.920 --> 18:27.580
have a date with someone else?

18:28.730 --> 18:30.200
Mr. Ji, you're drunk.

18:33.320 --> 18:34.150
Maybe.

18:43.550 --> 18:44.640
Mrs. Nie.

18:49.830 --> 18:51.740
What's so strange about this?

18:52.340 --> 18:54.160
When the husband
has a little affair or two,

18:54.160 --> 18:55.510
you just turn a blind eye

18:55.510 --> 18:56.440
and let it pass.

18:56.690 --> 18:59.400
Nie Yucheng is the one
making money to support their family.

18:59.400 --> 19:01.290
What could she possibly complain about?

19:01.290 --> 19:02.400
Don't tell me

19:02.480 --> 19:04.210
she'd dare to ask for a divorce.

19:04.480 --> 19:05.320
Mrs. Gu.

19:10.720 --> 19:12.030
It really is you.

19:12.440 --> 19:13.510
I saw you over there just now,

19:13.510 --> 19:14.840
and I thought it was you.

19:14.880 --> 19:16.600
We haven't seen each other
for a long time, Mrs. Nie.

19:16.600 --> 19:17.390
Cheers.

19:23.110 --> 19:24.510
I heard from my husband before

19:24.510 --> 19:26.290
that he saw you at the team building.

19:26.290 --> 19:27.920
He said you are
very different from before.

19:27.920 --> 19:29.890
Seeing you today, it's indeed true.

19:29.890 --> 19:31.830
-Mrs. Nie...
-I've already divorced Nie Yucheng.

19:31.830 --> 19:33.760
You couldn't not know that, right?

19:35.920 --> 19:37.490
Who wouldn't know?

19:37.510 --> 19:38.590
I'm sorry.

19:38.800 --> 19:39.820
It just slipped out.

19:39.820 --> 19:41.200
I'm used to calling you that.

19:41.200 --> 19:41.960
Sorry.

19:44.330 --> 19:45.620
Who is this?

19:45.640 --> 19:47.690
Aren't you going to introduce him to me?

19:47.690 --> 19:50.550
This is Mr. Ji,
the general manager of Purong Hotel.

19:54.130 --> 19:54.920
Mrs...

19:56.100 --> 19:57.370
You moved on so fast

19:57.400 --> 19:59.730
and are with such a powerful figure again.

20:00.470 --> 20:02.580
Did he bring you to the party today?

20:03.650 --> 20:04.970
Next time I see you,

20:05.000 --> 20:07.280
should I call you Mrs. Ji?

20:08.570 --> 20:09.900
Don't be shy.

20:11.720 --> 20:12.410
Madam,

20:12.480 --> 20:13.750
you might have misunderstood.

20:13.750 --> 20:15.480
Let me introduce her to you again.

20:15.480 --> 20:17.620
She is the lobby manager of Purong Hotel.

20:17.620 --> 20:19.410
It was Marcos, the host of today's party,

20:19.410 --> 20:20.340
who invited her.

20:20.360 --> 20:22.490
She wasn't brought in by someone else.

20:22.760 --> 20:23.590
I...

20:24.730 --> 20:26.290
Whatever past you may have,

20:26.320 --> 20:27.810
please show some respect.

20:27.880 --> 20:29.240
How was I disrespectful to her?

20:29.240 --> 20:30.030
Then you must not remember

20:30.030 --> 20:31.400
what my name is.

20:31.400 --> 20:33.390
It's fine. Let's get
to know each other again.

20:33.390 --> 20:34.560
I am not Mrs. Nie,

20:34.580 --> 20:35.760
nor Mrs. Ji,

20:35.780 --> 20:37.190
nor anyone's wife.

20:37.410 --> 20:39.220
My name is Xu Miyu.

20:39.250 --> 20:40.250
Nice to meet you.

20:47.110 --> 20:47.680
I...

20:52.950 --> 20:53.470
Miyu.

20:59.480 --> 21:01.380
You left your phone earlier.

21:01.410 --> 21:02.430
I wanted to return it to you.

21:02.430 --> 21:03.110
Thank you.

21:04.970 --> 21:06.230
Thank you for earlier.

21:06.330 --> 21:07.260
You're welcome.

21:17.010 --> 21:19.550
I look forward to working with you.

21:19.920 --> 21:20.640
Excuse me.

21:23.490 --> 21:24.430
How was it?

21:24.610 --> 21:25.660
Did you have fun?

21:25.680 --> 21:27.240
Thank you for your hospitality today.

21:27.240 --> 21:28.600
I had a great time.

21:28.750 --> 21:30.060
Does that mean...

21:30.680 --> 21:31.610
You're leaving?

21:31.700 --> 21:34.190
I'm afraid I can't stay till the end.

21:34.520 --> 21:36.090
I won't keep you then.

21:36.110 --> 21:37.310
When I go to Purong Hotel,

21:37.310 --> 21:38.050
we'll meet again.

21:38.050 --> 21:40.050
Okay, have fun.

21:40.800 --> 21:41.430
Thanks.

21:43.340 --> 21:44.100
Kenny.

21:51.350 --> 21:52.420
I'll take you back.

21:52.960 --> 21:53.590
Mr. Ji.

21:55.160 --> 21:56.270
You don't need to take me back.

21:56.270 --> 21:57.400
I'll go back myself.

22:01.140 --> 22:01.790
Okay.

22:40.060 --> 22:42.250
♪ I know at the start of every story ♪

22:43.140 --> 22:45.050
♪ They all feel somewhat the same ♪

22:47.120 --> 22:49.320
♪ Just never thought I would ♪

22:50.340 --> 22:52.250
♪ Fall for you so deeply ♪

22:54.000 --> 22:56.390
♪ Why did I have to lose myself? ♪

22:56.920 --> 22:59.070
♪ In the virtual world ♪

23:00.420 --> 23:05.680
♪ Unfinished dreams hurt the most ♪

23:07.350 --> 23:09.220
♪ Like a moth drawn to the flame ♪

23:09.760 --> 23:13.140
♪ Wandering aimlessly
through the night sky ♪

23:14.650 --> 23:16.240
♪ Until I met you ♪

23:17.040 --> 23:20.210
♪ Like fire that finally took my life ♪

23:20.720 --> 23:22.680
♪ I thought my deep devotion
and sincerity ♪

23:23.140 --> 23:24.870
♪ Would earn your eternal loyalty ♪

23:24.320 --> 23:25.070
Sorry, Sir.

23:25.070 --> 23:26.190
Let me change your...

23:25.330 --> 23:26.630
♪ Because you are like a cloud ♪

23:26.670 --> 23:27.870
It's you?

23:26.950 --> 23:28.800
♪ I became a wisp of wind ♪

23:28.170 --> 23:29.540
Why are you here?

23:29.210 --> 23:32.210
♪ In the end, all the promises we made ♪

23:29.570 --> 23:30.700
Thanks to you,

23:31.300 --> 23:32.900
I am no longer Mrs. Nie now.

23:32.430 --> 23:34.010
♪ Turned into nothing but emptiness ♪

23:32.920 --> 23:33.880
If the previous guest

23:33.880 --> 23:36.100
left something indecent

23:34.990 --> 23:36.770
♪ Once, for your dream ♪

23:36.130 --> 23:37.470
and blamed it on me,

23:36.980 --> 23:38.670
♪ I gritted my teeth
and pushed myself forward ♪

23:37.560 --> 23:38.840
I won't be able to explain it.

23:38.840 --> 23:39.880
If you hadn't

23:39.450 --> 23:41.650
♪ Love really hurts ♪

23:39.880 --> 23:41.370
helped my ex-husband lie to me,

23:41.370 --> 23:42.300
would my life now

23:42.310 --> 23:43.880
be reduced to this?

23:42.880 --> 23:47.540
♪ I never thought I could be so brave ♪

23:43.880 --> 23:45.590
Didn't you say
I have pitifully little empathy?

23:45.590 --> 23:47.950
I'm sorry, I shouldn't
have said that about you.

23:47.950 --> 23:49.030
I found it.

23:50.960 --> 23:51.810
Mr. Ji,

23:51.840 --> 23:53.450
are you satisfied with my service?

23:53.450 --> 23:55.640
If you are satisfied,
please give me a good review.

23:55.640 --> 23:56.440
Thank you.

23:56.960 --> 23:58.970
If my appeal gets no result,

24:00.180 --> 24:02.150
♪ Like a moth drawn to the flame ♪

24:00.700 --> 24:02.440
where can I find you
to return the money to you?

24:02.440 --> 24:03.410
You're being this proactive.

24:02.480 --> 24:05.840
♪ Wandering aimlessly
through the night sky ♪

24:04.050 --> 24:05.130
Aren't you afraid that he'll target you?

24:05.130 --> 24:06.280
You said

24:06.310 --> 24:07.470
we must work together as a team.

24:07.470 --> 24:09.090
♪ Until I met you ♪

24:09.860 --> 24:13.270
♪ Like fire that finally took my life ♪

24:09.900 --> 24:10.570
I can't help it.

24:10.570 --> 24:11.840
It's your first time being a forewoman.

24:11.840 --> 24:13.790
And it's my first time officially
being a general manager.

24:13.690 --> 24:15.660
♪ I thought my deep devotion
and sincerity ♪

24:14.640 --> 24:15.920
Let's help each other

24:16.000 --> 24:17.790
♪ Would earn your eternal loyalty ♪

24:16.180 --> 24:17.510
and support each other.

24:18.170 --> 24:19.430
♪ Because you are like a cloud ♪

24:19.780 --> 24:21.590
♪ I became a wisp of wind ♪

24:21.960 --> 24:24.980
♪ In the end, all the promises we made ♪

24:25.310 --> 24:26.830
♪ Turned into nothing but emptiness ♪

24:27.930 --> 24:29.510
♪ Once, for your dream ♪

24:29.790 --> 24:31.520
♪ I gritted my teeth
and pushed myself forward ♪

24:32.370 --> 24:34.500
♪ Love really hurts ♪

24:35.530 --> 24:40.200
♪ I never thought I could be so brave ♪

24:39.390 --> 24:42.700
Why do you work as an attendant at Purong?

24:42.920 --> 24:45.030
With your knowledge and ability,

24:43.700 --> 24:46.420
♪ Only when you've been hurt by love
do you realize how crazy you once were ♪

24:45.060 --> 24:47.540
you should go to a bigger platform

24:46.920 --> 24:49.840
♪ A beautiful dream
turns into a nightmare in an instant ♪

24:47.560 --> 24:50.190
to do work that better reflects
your personal value.

24:50.190 --> 24:52.340
Mr. Ji, may I ask you
a question in return?

24:51.090 --> 24:55.980
♪ You are a neon light
I could never catch ♪

24:52.920 --> 24:54.110
In what capacity

24:54.110 --> 24:55.970
are you saying these things to me?

24:56.950 --> 24:58.870
♪ I loved you recklessly ♪

25:00.250 --> 25:02.620
♪ And ended up covered in wounds ♪

25:03.690 --> 25:04.980
♪ Yet I still believe in ♪

25:04.620 --> 25:07.050
[Tan Jizhou]

25:04.750 --> 25:06.640
Miyu, I've arrived in Shanghai.

25:05.990 --> 25:08.540
♪ The sky after the rain ♪

25:06.680 --> 25:07.830
Can we meet?

25:10.060 --> 25:12.060
♪ I thought my deep devotion
and sincerity ♪

25:12.430 --> 25:14.060
♪ Would earn your eternal loyalty ♪

25:14.600 --> 25:15.860
♪ Because you are like a cloud ♪

25:16.210 --> 25:17.970
♪ I became a wisp of wind ♪

25:18.380 --> 25:21.410
♪ In the end, all the promises we made ♪

25:21.740 --> 25:23.330
♪ Turned into nothing but emptiness ♪

25:24.350 --> 25:25.910
♪ Once, for your dream ♪

25:26.220 --> 25:27.960
♪ I gritted my teeth
and pushed myself forward ♪

25:27.680 --> 25:28.490
Sir,

25:28.810 --> 25:30.920
♪ Love really hurts ♪

25:29.240 --> 25:31.440
please drive a bit faster.

25:31.460 --> 25:32.190
Okay.

25:31.970 --> 25:36.640
♪ I never thought I could be so brave ♪

25:39.790 --> 25:48.060
♪ In the end, everything came to nothing ♪

25:55.400 --> 25:57.030
Sir, your keys.

25:57.440 --> 25:58.100
Thank you.

26:25.080 --> 26:26.380
W-Why are you here?

26:28.150 --> 26:30.150
Weren't you going to see Tan Jizhou?

26:30.350 --> 26:31.310
Who told you...

26:32.460 --> 26:33.870
Did you check my phone?

26:34.280 --> 26:35.940
Sorry, I didn't mean to.

26:36.410 --> 26:37.810
I just saw it by accident.

26:38.650 --> 26:40.690
You thought I went to see Tan Jizhou.

26:41.090 --> 26:42.890
Why did you come to my dorm?

26:43.530 --> 26:45.010
I just came to wait for you.

26:46.270 --> 26:47.730
What if I didn't come back?

26:48.290 --> 26:50.220
I would keep waiting

26:51.240 --> 26:52.790
until you came back.

26:54.720 --> 26:56.850
Why did you let yourself get like this?

26:58.920 --> 27:00.070
Don't you know?

27:02.170 --> 27:03.800
Because I like you.

27:08.200 --> 27:09.060
What about you?

27:11.960 --> 27:13.290
You're drunk, Ji Feng.

27:12.290 --> 27:14.200
♪ Life is full of ♪

27:14.750 --> 27:15.940
I'm not drunk.

27:15.250 --> 27:17.900
♪ Countless crossroads ♪

27:16.800 --> 27:18.720
I know what I'm saying.

27:19.280 --> 27:21.450
I know I missed the best opportunity.

27:19.430 --> 27:23.280
♪ Chase joy too hard, and it slips away ♪

27:21.810 --> 27:23.540
I don't want to miss it again.

27:24.000 --> 27:25.260
Tell me

27:24.870 --> 27:26.870
♪ All those confusions ♪

27:25.980 --> 27:27.240
how you feel.

27:27.460 --> 27:31.180
♪ No answers, no reasons ♪

27:29.130 --> 27:30.250
I have to go.

27:32.060 --> 27:36.060
♪ Throwing ourselves
into the tide of the unknown ♪

27:39.460 --> 27:41.820
♪ Knowing when to advance or retreat,
yet still asleep ♪

27:39.780 --> 27:42.110
Why is it that every time
I get close to you,

27:42.270 --> 27:43.900
you step back?

27:42.990 --> 27:45.060
♪ Rushing to ripen before our time ♪

27:44.940 --> 27:47.480
Why can’t you admit that you like me?

27:46.740 --> 27:50.640
♪ Sighing at partings,
who meets whom at which crossing ♪

27:52.260 --> 27:54.190
♪ Busy and restless ♪

27:54.660 --> 27:58.460
♪ No turning back, no stopping ♪

27:59.440 --> 28:03.580
♪ Our path—do you see it now ♪

28:05.380 --> 28:07.950
♪ Just lift your head, oh ♪

28:09.060 --> 28:11.150
♪ Don't look back ♪

28:12.060 --> 28:13.980
♪ I've already learned ♪

28:14.610 --> 28:18.590
♪ If it's not mine, I won't force it ♪

28:19.140 --> 28:21.020
♪ No matter how you force it ♪

28:21.600 --> 28:25.940
♪ It'll only turn into a long,
endless wait ♪

28:26.520 --> 28:29.650
♪ Waiting to make peace with myself ♪

28:30.460 --> 28:32.780
♪ And waiting to meet someone again ♪

28:33.380 --> 28:35.330
♪ Wave goodbye ♪

28:48.090 --> 28:50.580
♪ Knowing when to advance or retreat,
yet still asleep ♪

28:51.390 --> 28:53.390
♪ Rushing to ripen before our time ♪

28:55.370 --> 28:59.570
♪ Sighing at partings,
who meets whom at which crossing ♪

29:00.890 --> 29:02.980
♪ Busy and restless ♪

29:03.290 --> 29:07.270
♪ No turning back, no stopping ♪

29:08.070 --> 29:12.330
♪ Our path—do you see it now ♪

29:14.280 --> 29:15.960
♪ No matter how you force it ♪

29:16.740 --> 29:21.190
♪ It'll only turn into a long,
endless wait ♪

29:21.660 --> 29:24.470
♪ Waiting to make peace with myself ♪

29:25.600 --> 29:27.920
♪ And waiting to meet someone again ♪

29:28.520 --> 29:30.330
♪ Wave goodbye ♪

29:39.250 --> 29:42.110
[Purong Hotel]

29:43.830 --> 29:44.610
Morning, Ms. Xu.

29:44.610 --> 29:45.210
Morning.

29:57.240 --> 29:58.160
Ms. An.

29:59.680 --> 30:00.770
Miyu.

30:03.010 --> 30:04.750
This outfit really suits you.

30:05.030 --> 30:05.890
It looks great.

30:06.160 --> 30:07.000
Thank you.

30:07.610 --> 30:09.260
How is your recovery going?

30:09.590 --> 30:11.360
I've heard
the postpartum period is really tough.

30:11.360 --> 30:12.350
Tell me about it.

30:13.920 --> 30:15.070
I never expected

30:15.130 --> 30:17.240
being a mother
requires so many sacrifices.

30:17.240 --> 30:18.370
I'm breastfeeding.

30:18.650 --> 30:20.070
Since my baby was born,

30:20.100 --> 30:22.030
I haven't had a full night's sleep.

30:22.160 --> 30:24.790
Then what will you do
now that you're back at work?

30:24.790 --> 30:25.510
The hotel,

30:25.510 --> 30:27.720
out of care for me as a new mother,

30:27.830 --> 30:28.920
gave me a choice.

30:29.510 --> 30:31.800
I could be transferred
to the executive office as a manager,

30:31.800 --> 30:33.200
with the same rank and benefits,

30:33.200 --> 30:35.060
working a nine-to-five desk job.

30:35.400 --> 30:36.680
It would be much easier.

30:36.680 --> 30:38.000
You'd have more time

30:38.000 --> 30:39.530
to take care of your family.

30:41.000 --> 30:42.030
But I

30:42.480 --> 30:44.970
still chose to come back
as a lobby manager.

30:47.170 --> 30:49.350
The lobby is where I started.

30:50.180 --> 30:52.510
I've been in the Front Office
since I joined,

30:52.510 --> 30:54.680
and became a lobby manager
in three years.

30:54.680 --> 30:57.210
Although I had the chance
to work in an office,

30:57.640 --> 30:58.790
I didn't like it.

30:59.960 --> 31:01.400
I was born to worry,

31:01.560 --> 31:03.420
and I like being the chief butler.

31:04.440 --> 31:05.850
So in the end,

31:06.310 --> 31:07.750
you choose your own path.

31:08.970 --> 31:11.130
Since I can choose to do what I love,

31:11.210 --> 31:13.270
what does it matter if it's a bit hard?

31:13.940 --> 31:15.810
I don't want my baby to think

31:15.990 --> 31:16.920
that his mother

31:16.940 --> 31:19.870
doesn't even have
the courage to face difficulties.

31:20.370 --> 31:21.200
Ms. An.

31:21.460 --> 31:22.180
Keep it up.

31:23.810 --> 31:24.770
You too.

31:25.200 --> 31:27.370
You look gentle,

31:27.760 --> 31:29.490
but you're very strong inside.

31:30.080 --> 31:33.190
Watching you go from housekeeping
to the front desk step by step,

31:33.190 --> 31:35.870
and maybe even higher
and further in the future,

31:36.770 --> 31:38.790
I feel greatly encouraged.

31:42.000 --> 31:44.960
[Jiang Zhichun]

31:43.480 --> 31:44.680
Are you free tonight?

31:45.000 --> 31:45.890
Let's meet up.

31:46.260 --> 31:47.560
I need to talk to you.

31:50.370 --> 31:52.430
The news lately has been terrifying.

31:52.950 --> 31:54.610
It puts everyone in a bad mood.

31:55.130 --> 31:56.650
Someone died here.

31:57.040 --> 31:59.120
[Are you free tonight? Let's meet up.
I need to talk to you]

31:57.120 --> 31:58.920
This used to be a popular photo spot.

31:58.920 --> 31:59.720
Now look at it.

31:59.740 --> 32:01.000
No one dares to go.

32:01.400 --> 32:02.200
What's wrong?

32:04.680 --> 32:06.430
There is a top-rated scenic spot

32:06.430 --> 32:08.690
with a glass walkway tens of meters long.

32:08.850 --> 32:10.200
[Glass Walkway Failure
Causes a Tourist to Fall Down Mountain]

32:09.480 --> 32:10.680
It allegedly malfunctioned,

32:10.220 --> 32:11.360
[Famed Foliage
and Snow Destination in Crisis]

32:10.700 --> 32:12.530
causing a tourist to fall off the cliff.

32:11.390 --> 32:12.240
[Recently at the famous
top-rated scenic spot,]

32:12.260 --> 32:13.370
[a heartbreaking accident occurred]

32:13.240 --> 32:15.240
This place used to be super crowded.

32:15.350 --> 32:16.310
People enjoyed the snow in winter,

32:16.310 --> 32:17.710
and the leaves in autumn.

32:17.850 --> 32:18.440
Right.

32:18.750 --> 32:20.750
Dianjiangchun promoted this place before.

32:20.750 --> 32:22.950
Maybe she's the one who made it popular.

32:23.680 --> 32:24.240
Really?

32:24.480 --> 32:25.270
Look.

32:25.270 --> 32:28.600
Why is everyone mentioning
Dianjiangchun in the comments?

32:30.960 --> 32:32.580
The scenic spot had an accident.

32:32.580 --> 32:33.860
Why are they scolding the blogger?

32:32.890 --> 32:33.430
[Comments]

32:33.450 --> 32:34.540
[Dianjiangchun, don't you
have any responsibility?]

32:34.560 --> 32:35.300
[Doesn't your conscience bother you?]

32:37.070 --> 32:38.100
[Unknown Caller]

32:42.800 --> 32:43.880
Some netizens are going too far.

32:43.880 --> 32:44.400
Hello.

32:44.610 --> 32:46.560
Mr. Ji, could you please come over?

32:47.430 --> 32:48.150
What is it?

32:48.740 --> 32:50.540
Zhichun is being cyberbullied.

32:50.880 --> 32:51.960
The board is going to abandon her.

32:51.960 --> 32:53.270
None of us can reach her right now.

32:53.270 --> 32:55.330
I had no choice but to ask you for help.

32:55.440 --> 32:57.360
Okay, don't worry.

32:57.380 --> 32:58.510
I'll be right there.

33:00.950 --> 33:03.690
[Jiang Zhichun]

33:05.640 --> 33:07.000
I'm heading out for a bit.

33:07.000 --> 33:08.600
Call me if you need anything.

33:37.710 --> 33:38.510
Zhichun.

33:42.670 --> 33:44.110
I was wondering before,

33:46.090 --> 33:47.570
if I disappeared,

33:50.050 --> 33:53.010
would you be the first one to look for me?

33:54.960 --> 33:56.430
It seems I was right.

33:57.320 --> 33:58.760
On my way here,

33:59.180 --> 34:00.980
I learned about the whole thing.

34:01.600 --> 34:03.150
Can you come down first?

34:07.320 --> 34:08.170
Look,

34:08.190 --> 34:11.239
[Resolution on the Change
of a Partner of Qiguang Media Co., Ltd.]

34:09.330 --> 34:11.320
I can't even rely on a promise

34:12.219 --> 34:14.150
that's written in black and white.

34:24.600 --> 34:25.989
How ironic.

34:26.409 --> 34:28.739
I've been an influencer for so many years,

34:28.770 --> 34:30.699
and this is the first time I realize

34:31.500 --> 34:33.500
the weight of the word "influence".

34:33.639 --> 34:34.969
The Jiang Zhichun I know

34:36.210 --> 34:37.650
would never give up so easily.

34:37.650 --> 34:39.070
You've made it this far.

34:39.340 --> 34:41.600
Are you really afraid of cyberbullying?

34:41.820 --> 34:43.679
I'm not afraid of cyberbullying.

34:44.719 --> 34:45.870
But some people are.

34:47.650 --> 34:48.730
Can you imagine?

34:49.850 --> 34:52.030
The partners you spend every day with,

34:52.030 --> 34:53.489
once they are on the board,

34:54.290 --> 34:55.429
drop their smiles

34:56.670 --> 34:59.000
and try to strip you
of your partner title.

35:00.550 --> 35:03.180
I founded this company myself.

35:03.470 --> 35:05.250
Why should I be pushed out?

35:05.410 --> 35:06.860
Why should I be the sacrifice?

35:06.860 --> 35:08.130
Exactly, why?

35:08.750 --> 35:10.830
Giving up on yourself here

35:10.910 --> 35:12.690
doesn't hurt them at all.

35:13.320 --> 35:15.580
You, Jiang Zhichun, are so competitive.

35:15.630 --> 35:18.190
In the past, you were always
the one who did the leaving.

35:18.190 --> 35:20.630
Are you willing to become a discard now?

35:23.290 --> 35:24.290
Don't worry.

35:26.440 --> 35:27.540
Jiang Zhichun

35:28.970 --> 35:31.500
won't easily become
someone else's discard.

35:54.150 --> 35:54.960
Ji Feng.

35:56.690 --> 35:57.650
I'm sorry.

35:58.320 --> 36:01.580
I've thought about it
countless times recently.

36:04.030 --> 36:06.320
If only I weren't so selfish.

36:09.650 --> 36:12.210
If only I could turn back time.

36:21.600 --> 36:25.790
[Director Tang]

36:23.030 --> 36:24.000
Director Tang.

36:24.190 --> 36:25.340
How does the internal transfer process

36:25.340 --> 36:27.540
work between departments at our hotel?

36:34.850 --> 36:39.810
[Director Tang]

36:35.380 --> 36:37.430
Ms. Xu, do you want to transfer?

36:37.630 --> 36:39.000
If you want to transfer
from your position,

36:39.000 --> 36:40.400
it requires
the general manager's approval.

36:40.400 --> 36:41.190
Oh my god.

36:41.360 --> 36:42.320
Mr. Ji and Dianjiangchun

36:42.320 --> 36:43.920
are not really together, are they?

36:43.920 --> 36:45.280
Of course they are.

36:45.510 --> 36:48.970
They have been going in and out
of the same apartment together.

36:54.140 --> 36:55.890
[Dianjiangchun]

36:58.920 --> 36:59.400
[Following the sudden accident caused
by the glass walkway malfunction,]

36:59.420 --> 36:59.850
[the issue gained traction online,
and influencer]

36:59.880 --> 37:00.190
[Dianjiangchun
was thrust into the spotlight.]

37:00.220 --> 37:01.460
[As the public awaited her response
to questions about the promotion,]

37:01.480 --> 37:02.950
[a set of photos quickly
spread online, showing]

37:02.970 --> 37:04.450
[Dianjiangchun and Ji Feng entering
and leaving a luxury apartment together.]

37:04.470 --> 37:05.070
[Netizens questioned whether,
during the promotion, Dianjiangchun]

37:05.100 --> 37:05.780
[had thoroughly assessed
the safety of the site's facilities,]

37:05.800 --> 37:06.600
[and whether her promotional content
may have misled consumers.]

37:37.520 --> 37:38.080
I...

37:41.770 --> 37:42.750
Listen to me.

37:44.090 --> 37:45.980
I made things clear to her today.

37:46.880 --> 37:47.320
Between the two of us...

37:47.320 --> 37:47.920
Then why were you

37:47.920 --> 37:48.880
photographed going in

37:48.880 --> 37:50.440
and out of her apartment?

37:50.510 --> 37:52.150
Is this what you mean
by making things clear?

37:52.150 --> 37:54.080
I was afraid you'd misunderstand.

37:54.320 --> 37:55.840
It was an emergency today.

37:56.120 --> 37:58.030
Her assistant called me to help.

37:58.130 --> 38:00.480
I didn't expect it
to blow up like this online.

38:00.480 --> 38:04.070
-Trust me, between us...
-This isn't the first time this has happened.

38:04.070 --> 38:05.630
If drawing a clear line with your ex

38:05.630 --> 38:07.230
is this hard for you,

38:07.230 --> 38:08.800
maybe you should ask yourself

38:08.800 --> 38:10.800
whether you still have feelings for her.

38:10.800 --> 38:12.130
It's not what you think.

38:12.510 --> 38:13.480
Listen to my explanation.

38:13.480 --> 38:15.150
Enough, you don't need to say anything.

38:15.150 --> 38:17.350
Actually, there's nothing to explain.

38:17.440 --> 38:18.920
We are both adults.

38:19.000 --> 38:20.860
You are single, and I am divorced.

38:22.880 --> 38:25.340
If this is the kind
of relationship you want,

38:26.400 --> 38:28.000
you can just tell me clearly.

38:30.070 --> 38:30.670
By the way,

38:31.230 --> 38:32.280
I will probably submit an application

38:32.280 --> 38:34.630
for a cross-department transfer soon.

38:34.880 --> 38:37.080
Mr. Ji, you will need to approve it then.

38:49.150 --> 38:50.480
What is wrong with me?

38:51.360 --> 38:53.440
Why did I say those things to him?

38:54.590 --> 38:57.090
I don't want to see myself
lose control like this.

38:57.090 --> 38:58.840
♪ A flicker of dim light ♪

38:58.440 --> 38:59.670
Maybe this is the reason why I'm afraid

38:59.670 --> 39:01.710
to fall in love with someone again.

39:00.600 --> 39:02.240
♪ A bowl of warm soup ♪

39:03.250 --> 39:05.710
Mr. Ji, were you acquainted
with Ms. Jiang before?

39:04.460 --> 39:06.240
♪ People in the city ♪

39:05.710 --> 39:06.920
We...

39:07.190 --> 39:10.130
♪ Squeezing into the hustle and bustle ♪

39:08.320 --> 39:09.780
Were college classmates.

39:10.030 --> 39:12.070
[Set aside longing for the past;
kindle a new fire and savor fresh tea]

39:12.060 --> 39:13.870
♪ The palms of time ♪

39:12.090 --> 39:13.100
[Enjoy poetry and wine
in the prime of life]

39:15.790 --> 39:18.830
♪ Grinding away the simple days ♪

39:18.420 --> 39:20.490
Are the two of you dating?

39:19.520 --> 39:22.050
♪ Sprinkling them into this busy world ♪

39:20.880 --> 39:22.000
We...

39:22.410 --> 39:23.410
Used to be in love.

39:23.460 --> 39:25.630
♪ To be tasted, bit by bit ♪

39:23.590 --> 39:24.510
What about me?

39:25.150 --> 39:26.240
Can't I ask you out?

39:27.220 --> 39:30.270
♪ Embracing this radiant world ♪

39:28.320 --> 39:29.550
Their creamy pasta

39:29.570 --> 39:30.850
is still your weakness, huh?

39:30.750 --> 39:33.780
♪ Keeps the heart from fading to grey ♪

39:31.990 --> 39:32.630
[Netizens questioned whether,
during the promotion, Dianjiangchun]

39:32.650 --> 39:33.470
[had thoroughly assessed
the safety of the site's facilities,]

39:33.490 --> 39:34.520
[and whether her promotional content
may have misled consumers.]

39:34.370 --> 39:37.490
♪ Life's joy, sorrow, cold, and warmth ♪

39:38.230 --> 39:40.850
♪ Intertwined within the mundane ♪

39:42.270 --> 39:45.460
♪ Let us bravely gather up ♪

39:45.340 --> 39:46.550
Don't you know?

39:46.130 --> 39:49.580
♪ The forgotten past ♪

39:48.930 --> 39:50.240
Because I like you.

39:50.490 --> 39:52.760
♪ Walking through this world ♪

39:54.410 --> 39:58.430
♪ Leaving no regrets behind ♪

39:59.070 --> 40:00.600
[Tan Jizhou]

40:01.490 --> 40:02.320
Hello.

40:03.200 --> 40:05.250
Miyu, can we talk?

40:18.350 --> 40:19.140
Mr. Tan.

40:19.630 --> 40:21.030
Last time you asked me out,

40:21.030 --> 40:22.230
I couldn't make it.

40:22.360 --> 40:23.110
I'm sorry.

40:24.600 --> 40:27.000
Actually, I should be
the one to apologize.

40:27.600 --> 40:28.890
In Hong Kong,

40:28.920 --> 40:31.400
I was too abrupt. I'm sorry.

40:32.640 --> 40:35.430
I drank too much that day too.

40:37.000 --> 40:39.280
Actually, I thought about it
for a long time after I went back.

40:39.280 --> 40:41.010
I got ahead of myself last time.

40:42.190 --> 40:44.480
Relationships should develop naturally.

40:44.480 --> 40:45.810
We should take our time.

40:48.880 --> 40:49.840
So, Miyu,

40:51.190 --> 40:51.840
may I...

40:52.880 --> 40:54.440
May I pursue you?

41:09.150 --> 41:10.760
I've actually imagined many times

41:10.760 --> 41:12.630
what it would be like if we were together.

41:12.630 --> 41:14.920
I could talk about art with you,

41:15.280 --> 41:17.360
take you to exhibitions
all over the world,

41:17.360 --> 41:19.220
and give you everything you want.

41:19.590 --> 41:20.510
All you need to do is stay

41:20.510 --> 41:21.630
by my side.

41:23.000 --> 41:23.880
So Miyu,

41:24.930 --> 41:26.130
can you give me a chance?
